            "name":"The Distance of a Day",
            "description":"David Horvitz\n\nAmerican artist David Horvitz is best known for making the internet a stage for his eccentric and interactive projects.",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/David+Horvitz.html",
