            "description":"Shanthamani Muddaiah\n\nShanthamani Muddaiah's practice is intimately linked to the physicality of the materials she employs.",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Shanthamani.html",
