            "name":"The Fluidity of Horizons",
            "description":"Parvathi Nayar\n\nParvathi Nayar's works are hyper-real yet abstract portraits of the world.",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Parvathi+Nayar.html",
