            "description":"Wendelien van Oldenborgh\n\nMaurits Script (2006) is a double-channel installation that connects a little-known moment in Netherland's colonial past to its present political landscape.",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Wendelien+van.html",
