            "description":"Prashant Pandey\n\nArtha (2014) is an installation in the shape of a diamond, a universal symbol of prosperity, wealth and vanity",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Prashant+Pandey.html",
            "majorminor":"50-50",
