         {
            "name":"orbital cascade_57-46",
            "description":"Michael Najjar\n\nNajjar's exhibit orbital cascade_57-46 (2013) is a video projection on the floor illustrating the imagined trajectories of thousands of pieces of manmade space junk floating in the Earth's orbit.",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Michael+Najjar.html",
