            "name":"Perpetual Stills",
            "description":"Punaloor Rajan\n\nHis personal quest resulted in what now constitutes a rare and unparalleled archive of photographs and video footage.",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Punaloor+Rajan.html",
