            "description":"Kwan Sheung Chi\n\nA work denied exhibition in China, A Flags-Raising-Lowering Ceremony at my home's clothes drying rack (2007) captures the city's chequered history of regime changes and illustrates with a sense of the absurd the identity confusions this has engendered.",
