            "description":"Pushpamala N\n\nDisplayed at the Biennale, the photographic work The Arrival of Vasco da Gama (after an 1898 painting by Jose Veloso Salgado) (2014) recreates an 1898 history painting Vasco da Gama perante o Samorim by Portuguese painter Jose Veloso Salgado which depicts Vasco da Gama's first meeting with the Zamorin of Calicut.",
