            "name":"Nautilus",
            "description":"Wim Delvoye\n\nA sculpture in the shape of the marine mollusk it is named after, Nautilus is made of steel that has been cut into delicate filigree using lasers.",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Wim+Delvoye.html",
