            "name":"Kaaba Pop-ups",
            "description":"Hamra Abbas\n\nKaaba Pop-ups (2014) is a series of 24 handmade sculptures in various shades of blue composed of paper that has been folded into intricate Islamic stalactite patterns.",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Hamra+Abbas.html",
