            "description":"Mona Hatoum\n\nRoutes AP (2003) is a playful intervention on maps found in in-flight magazines.",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Mona+Hatoum.html",
