            "name":"What If The Earth Stopped Spinning?",
            "description":"Michael Stevens,Vsauce\n\nIn videos that are displayed across the venues of the Biennale",
            "detailsurl":"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/elasticbeanstalk-us-west-2-060425629624/biennale/beacon-detail/Michael.html",
